text: The Nokia 8600 Luna is a mobile phone produced by Nokia. It has a stainless steel body, and weighs 140 grams. Nokia 8600 Luna, review, Damian Koh, CNET Asia, July 26, 2007. Accessed on line December 4, 2007. Features include: TFT display (240 x 320 pixels), 2 megapixel camera, video recording and streaming, digital music player, and FM radio. == References== == External links == * Nokia 8600, review, Ellis Benton, cnet.co.uk, July 6, 2007. 8600 Luna Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2007
